value.snippet: Offering a wellness centre and a spa area, the luxury Hyatt Regency Auckland Hotel is located near Highwic History Museum. The hotel’s Residences Tower comprises 90 rooms and suites with kitchen facilities and balconies -including studio suites, one-and two-bedroom suites and penthouses. This is in addition to the 268 rooms in the Regency Tower.
